    <h1 class="blog-title">Night Routine for Dewy, Soft Skin</h1>
    <div class="blog-meta">8 min read • Written by Nowshin • Glow Journal</div>

    <img class="blog-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3738349/pexels-photo-3738349.jpeg">

    <div class="blog-content">

      <p>
        Skincare shouldn’t feel like a chore — it should feel like a calming moment between you and your skin.  
        A little ritual where your hands slow down, your breathing softens, and your mind resets.  
      </p>

      <p>
        This night routine is the exact one that started my glow journey, long before NowAuraa existed.  
        I used to scrub my skin, overload it with actives, and then wonder why I felt irritated — inside and out.  
      </p>

      <div class="quote-box">
        “Your glow isn’t something you chase —  
        it’s something you build softly, slowly, with intention.”
      </div>

      <p>
        When I created NowAuraa, I wanted a space where skincare could feel soft, intentional, and empowering —  
        not overwhelming or confusing. This night routine represents the heart of that:  
        hydration, simplicity, and gentle consistency.
      </p>

      <p>
        I always begin by melting the day away with a gentle cleanser that doesn’t strip my skin.  
        Then comes my holy grail: a soothing toner that feels like cool water mixed with peace.  
        After that, I layer hydrating essences and a barrier-repairing moisturizer that leaves a silky glow.
      </p>

      <p>
        This routine isn’t about perfection.  
        It’s about showing up for your skin in a way that feels good to you.  
      </p>

    </div>

